#: xmms/equalizer.c:1677
msgid ""
"If \"Auto\" is enabled on the equalizer, xmms will try to load equalizer "
"presets like this:\n"
"1: Look for a preset file in the directory of the file we are about to "
"play.\n"
"2: Look for a directory preset file in the same directory.\n"
"3: Look for a preset saved with the \"auto-load\" feature\n"
"4: Finally, try to load the \"default\" preset"
msgstr ""
"Jei \"Auto\" yra įjungtas ekvalaizeryje, xmms bandys įkelti ekvalaizerio "
"presetus taip:\n"
"1: Ieškos preseto bylos kataloge, iš kurio grosime kūrinį.\n"
"2: Ieškos katalogo presetų bylos tame pat kataloge.\n"
"3: Ieškos preseto, išsaugoto su \"auto-load\" galimybe.\n"
"4. Galiausiai, bandys įkelti \"įprastą\" presetą."

